      "title": "Diesel ship is coming",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A ship loaded with 30,000 metric tons of diesel will arrive in Sri Lanka, the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation said.",
        "Meanwhile, it is noted that a lubricant oil ship had arrived in the country yesterday (13) night. (a)"
